      "description": "Looking for a solid, no-frills vehicle that gets you where you need to go? This car might be exactly what you're after! It's in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives dependably, though it does show noticeable wear on both the interior and exterior that you'd expect from a well-used vehicle. At this price point, you're getting reliable transportation without the premium cost. Come take it for a spin and see if it's the right fit for you!",
