    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Great Opportunity for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 Looking for a fixer-upper with potential? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it will need significant repairs before it's road-ready, and we're not sugarcoating that. However, for a skilled mechanic or an enthusiastic DIYer, this could be a rewarding project at a wallet-friendly entry point. Come take a look, ask all your questions, and decide if this is the right project for you!",
