    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent with any prospective buyer. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable rust, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with age and hard use. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention; it may start and run, but should not be considered reliable transportation without repair work. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs a parts vehicle. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, and buyers should factor in repair costs before purchasing. No warranties are offered, and the car is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable, Road-Ready & Great Value! \u2014 Here's a fantastic opportunity to get into a well-maintained vehicle that's ready to serve you for years to come! This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, the major systems are in solid working order, and it presents well both inside and out. You'll notice the normal signs of a car that's been driven and enjoyed \u2014 a minor blemish here or there \u2014 but nothing that gets in the way of a great ownership experience. Mechanically sound and dependable, this is the sweet spot for buyers who want quality without paying mint-condition prices. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading consistent with a vehicle that has seen regular use over the years. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 expect faded upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks; prospective buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or minor repairs may be needed in the near term. There are no major structural or safety concerns that we are aware of, but we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic before committing to a purchase. This is a solid, honest daily driver for a buyer who understands what they are getting and is comfortable with a vehicle that is functional rather than pristine.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car for the right buyer. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 you may notice a few small scratches and light scuffs here and there, but there are no significant dents or structural damage. The paint retains a decent shine overall. The interior is clean and functional, with some expected wear on high-contact areas like the seats and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately \u2014 all major systems are in working order. This is a solid everyday driver that will serve you dependably, and it's priced honestly to reflect its true condition.",
      "price": 33500.0,
